I met @tracymorgan almost a year ago at a Knicks game. I didn’t know he had an extensive art and memorabilia collection in his home. When he commissioned me to paint a portrait of him and his kids to commemorate his latest HBO special I was hype! I wasn’t expecting him to invite me into his home and call me “friend”. We sat and he discussed with me what’s most important in life. He shared with me his highs and lows and stressed the importance of family, friends and relationships. Tracy is def a real one.💯 I chose the pic of him looking at the painting to post first because it reminds me of the moment I unveiled this piece is his living room. He sighed  in happiness and said “ my babies” shoutout Tra Jr. and Maven, anyone who meets your father knows instantly how much your Dad loves you. 💯
